    prime_numbers = [num for num in numbers if num > 100 and num < 1000 and all((num % i != 0 for i in range(0, int(num ** 0.5) + 1)))]
    return [num for num in prime_numbers if num * reduce(lambda x, y: x * y, prime_numbers) > 1000000]
